detaileddescription.para: It contains the call ID, date & time at which the call took place and it's duration (0 if it wasn't answered). You can also know if video was enabled or not or if it was a conference, as well as it's average quality.

If needed, you can also create a fake LinphoneCallLog using linphone_core_create_call_log(), otherwise use linphone_core_get_call_logs() or even linphone_call_get_call_log() to get the log of an ongoing call.
